org.eclipse.incquery.tooling.ui.queryexplorer.content.matcher

Class ObservablePatternMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.incquery.tooling.ui.queryexplorer.content.matcher.ObservablePatternMatcher

  • public class ObservablePatternMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    A PatternMatcher is associated to every IncQueryMatcher which is annotated with PatternUI annotation. These elements will be the children of the top level elements in the treeviewer.
    Author:
    Tamas Szabo
